te>點睇american god入面個原理?<br />\n鬼同神係有人相信先會存在/好勁,無人信果d鬼同神就會唔存在/廢到好似呀木咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n勁同廢係相對，存在唔存在係絕對，至於感唔感受到同睇唔睇到佢地存在就係機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5045fcee7acf46281d14b3dbbf3689446e480bc6","tid":309563,"uid":36383,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:03:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一句：老鬼老鬼 wee wee wa wa 冚家縮沙，急急如律令"},{"pid":"f9db89ab909dcec4876833e494d636c79083c633","tid":309563,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用咩捉</blockquote><br />\n打鬼用朱古力，捉鬼用保鮮紙</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老鬼唔同普通鬼，佢地用人嘅形式存在，同行為如同鬼魅般不可思議。捉老鬼要等鬼門關大開先有機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442614b4db0ce0df64ca7b9ecd1fcdd3b21d9e88","tid":309563,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"捉過邊個大仙，你遇過最強嘅鬼有幾勁？最後點捉到佢？"},{"pid":"e98a2906a9581427d9d27c074cda213aa9e8b509","tid":309563,"uid":57643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"無啦啦做咩要捉人地"},{"pid":"e74af84558f9ca0bd3a7320afa443c79a2378ac4","tid":309563,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:12:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>捉過邊個大仙，你遇過最強嘅鬼有幾勁？最後點捉到佢？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔講得捉過邊個，因為大仙係唔會超渡到，一直係仙界輪迴，直到佢覺悟自己只係一個人，而唔係咩大仙，先可以重獲新生。<br />\n<br />\n見過最勁嘅老鬼可以反枱，同埋大聲喝斥後生仔。<br />\n<br />\n我冇捉到佢，但係呢隻老鬼姓鄭，聽講佢係仙界位高權重，邊係我呢啲道士仔捉到？"},{"pid":"26a874a5824fc8f61fadbd4503d1ffeed5588824","tid":309563,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:13:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無啦啦做咩要捉人地</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁你要問下佢地做咩無啦啦捉人黎出氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0212022b74a25ed9f4950de1e27fea370df2e431","tid":309563,"uid":54346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"未驚過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：超仙"},{"pid":"5759044c073fdd03c0db64ea30a9f05ed6632f37","tid":309563,"uid":11506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:03:17.000Z","msg":"邊隻老鬼最黑人憎"},{"pid":"afbbea18eb428a315ea63a33979c105a76e144ae","tid":309563,"uid":30123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T08:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第一句：老鬼老鬼 wee wee wa wa 冚家縮沙，急急如律令</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44e61c4fc4180fabcb9e8f9c8074302046b3b5c1","tid":309563,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:12:09.000Z","msg":"HKU Hell嘅明日之星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打破仙制"},{"pid":"be40f65cc62176f98e67f200319b74b1d7f96496","tid":309563,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:24:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>HKU Hell嘅明日之星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打破仙制</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />地獄嘅明日之星，搵個識破地獄嘅落去做啦，擔當唔起"},{"pid":"2e654a14c2660df11f8472f822d79048bf8a9031","tid":309563,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:24:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊隻老鬼最黑人憎</blockquote><br />\n你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1f80d9cea6c136ff5e5c8a3deda125eb67b37b","tid":309563,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-05T09:26:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未驚